    <refsect1 xml:id="description"><title>Description</title>
        <para>
            <function>inversesqrt</function> returns the inverse of the square root of <parameter>x</parameter>.
            i.e., the value <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:mfrac><mml:mn>1</mml:mn><mml:msqrt><mml:mi>x</mml:mi></mml:msqrt></mml:mfrac></mml:math></inlineequation>.
            Results are undefined if <inlineequation><mml:math xmlns:mml="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" overflow="scroll"><mml:apply><mml:leq definitionURL="" encoding=""/><mml:mi>x</mml:mi><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:apply></mml:math></inlineequation>.
        </para>
